Class Notification

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.Notification
Direct Known Subclasses:
BookingNotification, PromotionalNotification, WaitListNotification
public class Notification extends Object
Represents a notification sent to a system user. Tracks message content, recipient, delivery time, and read status.
Author:
team IOTA

    • Notification

      public Notification()

    • Notification

      public Notification(int notificationId, int userId, String message, String notificationType)
      Parameterized constructor for creating a new notification.
      Parameters:
      notificationId - unique persistent ID
      userId - target recipient user ID
      message - text content
      notificationType - category string
